BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:2026 Society of Environmental Journalists (SEJ) Conference
DTSTART;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260415T000000
DTEND;TZID=EDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260418T000000
UID:40d7e8ea6a695a52db7908b7908315cc@solutionsjournalism.org
DESCRIPTION:Chicago\, Illinois\, United States\nJoin us at Society of Envi
 ronmental Journalists' annual conference. This year's event explores how c
 limate\, water\, energy\, food\, agriculture and health intersect\, and ho
 w journalists can illuminate the systems that sustain life on our planet.\
 nMark your calendar for the Mapping the Future of Climate Journalism uncon
 ference workshop on Apr. 15. Together we’ll explore what climate journal
 ism needs in this moment\, building onThe Climate Blueprint for Media Tran
 sformation. An add-on ticket is required to attend.\nIn addition to the un
 conference session\, there are several more opportunities to participate i
 n solutions journalism workshops and conversations throughout the conferen
 ce:
LOCATION:Chicago\, Illinois\, United States
URL:https://www.sej2026.org/
X-SOURCE:Solutions Journalism Network
END:VEVENT
